name: Non Veg Supreme
description: This delectable pizza is made using generous amounts of black olives, onions, grilled chicken rashers, pepper BBQ chicken, and grilled mushrooms.

name: GOLDEN CORN PIZZA
description: A healthy pizza prepared with the goodness of sweet corn and cheese to give you that perfect satisfaction so order the Golden Corn Pizza from Domino's and you will fall in love with it.

name: JALAPENO AND RED PAPRIKA PIZZA
description: Pepper Barbeque Chicken I CheeseFeeling spicy? Add some heat to your favorite Domino's pizza with jalapeño peppers! Jalapeño peppers have a mild to medium spiciness. Barely visible through a layer of melted cheese, the pepper perks up the most basic of pizza pies.

name: MARGHERITA
description: Made using the freshest dough, 100% genuine mozzarella cheese, and chef's secret herbs, the Margehrita pizza Domino's tastes blissfully delicious. Though the classic version of the pizza doesn't have any other toppings than pure cheese, you can get the pizza customized by adding some toppings of your choice.

name: DOUBLE CHEESE MARGHERITA PIZZA
description: Our double cheese pizza comes with the goodness of extra cheese. You can see oodles of liquid cheese coming out with every bite, making the pizza all the more delicious.
